Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:42.02,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I only believe in the future, I don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:47.52,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,that racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:53.53,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,it's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:57.03,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:03.71,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I follow, follow in the footsteps of a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:06.98,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:10.27,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:22.33,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:25.39,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,of a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:31.40,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go with you, so passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:34.49,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I don't really need everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:37.84,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:41.08,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.21,0:01:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.96,0:01:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a Winter Island!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.26,0:02:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The name of those mountains \Nis the Drum Rockies.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.26,0:02:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In the castle on top of the \Ntallest mountain lives Dr. Kureha,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.68,0:02:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the only doctor in our country who is \Ncalled a "witch" by our country's people.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.32,0:02:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, Nami. Hang on tight.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.07,0:02:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.61,0:02:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.16,0:02:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out for Lapins.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.04,0:02:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're carnivorous, ferocious bunnies.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.80,0:02:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you run into a group of them, you're dead.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.92,0:02:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They have bodies like bears, \Nbut the agility of bunnies...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.10,0:02:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and they attack in groups.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.18,0:02:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.03,0:02:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What're they doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.33,0:03:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Those damn bunnies... \NThis can't be happening...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.16,0:03:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sanji. What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.62,0:03:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... we're gonna run, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:24.68,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(264,110)}Dalton's Resolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:24.68,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\fs55\pos(401.5,455)}Wapol's Corps \NLands On The Island
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.68,0:03:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Run? Where to?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter where! Someplace far!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.86,0:03:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.02,0:03:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,An avalanche...! An avalanche is coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.41,0:03:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! Those damn bunnies! \NThey'll never get away with this! Dammit!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.99,0:03:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-Wh-What're we gonna do?! \NWh-Wh-What're we gonna do, Sanji?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.08,0:03:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know?! \NThe first priority is Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.42,0:03:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The second is Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}! \NThe third is Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.88,0:03:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The fourth is Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}! \NAnd the fifth is Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.54,0:03:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Got that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.22,0:03:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect her even if it kills you!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.38,0:04:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.09,0:04:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there! That cliff!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.39,0:04:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Cliff?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.48,0:04:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! We need to get as high up as we can!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.06,0:04:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, we made... Ahh!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.09,0:04:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! We're not high enough!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.30,0:04:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wapol...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.88,0:04:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wapol came back!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.06,0:04:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.38,0:04:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0} headed to Big Horn!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.06,0:04:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who can fight, grab a \Nweapon and head to Big Horn!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.23,0:05:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! \NThose who can fight, head to Big Horn!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.39,0:05:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.48,0:05:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wapol came back!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.57,0:05:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, grab a weapon!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.87,0:05:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll protect our country!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.12,0:05:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab a weapon! Head to Big Horn!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.54,0:05:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.96,0:05:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Vivi. \NAre you really sure this is the right direction
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.21,0:05:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Gyasta town where the witch is right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.46,0:05:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm... \NWhen you put it that way, I'm not really sure...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.88,0:05:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in trouble if you aren't sure...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.18,0:05:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, if Luffy and Sanji \Nmanaged to get to the castle
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.64,0:05:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and didn't find the doctor, \Nthey'd think, "What're we doing?"
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.64,0:05:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless we find the doctor soon and \Nask her to go back to the castle...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.19,0:05:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.62,0:05:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know that, then do something. \NYou're a princess, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.07,0:05:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That has nothing to do with this. \NI'm not a witch. I'm a princess.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.41,0:05:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.53,0:05:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you look at the map.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.83,0:05:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.58,0:05:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's snow everywhere. The map is...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, you don't know...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.99,0:06:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I don't know at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be proud!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.92,0:06:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, there should be \Na sign for Gyasta on this route.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.05,0:06:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't miss it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.47,0:06:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. Leave it to me! \NI'll watch for signs of the sign!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.76,0:06:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, ignoring me, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.74,0:06:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.92,0:06:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, citizens!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.12,0:06:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything in this country is my snack!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm great!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.67,0:06:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuromarimo, tell them!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.04,0:06:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you're the king, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.21,0:06:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.30,0:06:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly right! \NIf I wanna eat a house,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.63,0:06:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing like one cooked \Nwell-done to a golden-brown after all!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wapol-{\i1}sama{\i0}. \NI have some information for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.68,0:06:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.84,0:06:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I received a report that some of the Straw Hats
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.69,0:07:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,rudely headed towards Drum Castle.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.02,0:07:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that they took a sick woman \Nto have her treated by a doctor.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Such idiots!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.03,0:07:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No one lives in my castle now, \Nnot to mention a doctor!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.91,0:07:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well... \NI heard that the outrageous Dr. Kureha
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.25,0:07:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,even more rudely currently lives in Drum Castle...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.75,0:07:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! \NThat old hag's living in my castle?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how much does she intend to mock me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.47,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kick her out!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.35,0:07:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Along with Straw Hat, I'll eat her up!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.77,0:07:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Men, we're going back to the castle!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.90,0:07:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.86,0:07:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.95,0:07:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! I was cut down! I'm gonna die!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.49,0:07:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.79,0:08:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here to kill you. \NYou dying suits me just fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.29,0:08:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard, Dalton!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.75,0:08:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're alive!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you hurt Wapol-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.71,0:08:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't be a big deal...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.05,0:08:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,with the excellent doctors of our country,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.34,0:08:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the "great medical care nation" Drum.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.72,0:08:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.35,0:08:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Twenty MDs External Injury Unit! \NCome forward!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.68,0:08:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting an operation.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.56,0:08:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting an operation.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.60,0:08:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting an operation.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.52,0:08:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting an operation.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.44,0:08:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting an operation.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.52,0:08:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting an operation.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.56,0:08:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting an operation.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.65,0:08:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Scalpel!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.40,0:08:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Needle!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.03,0:08:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tin.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.61,0:08:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hammer.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.40,0:08:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I really thought I'd die!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.11,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like what happened now,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.62,0:08:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you're the only one protected \Nand citizens have no choice
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.49,0:08:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but to suffer from sickness \Nwithout seeing doctors... Wapol!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.17,0:08:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wapol?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.54,0:08:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Wapol-{\i1}sama{\i0}, my retainer Dalton.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.30,0:08:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right! \NYou don't have the right to blather!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.59,0:08:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of us, you included, \Nwere Wapol-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s top brass.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.84,0:08:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We were his loyal hands, remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.43,0:09:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that when you \Nwere making people suffer,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.18,0:09:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,all I could do was just watch
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.39,0:09:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,even though I was by your \Nside as one of your top brass.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.15,0:09:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to take responsibility for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wapol...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.82,0:09:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's leave this country together.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.61,0:09:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We must not stay in this land any longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.86,0:09:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0}! You didn't do anything wrong!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.79,0:09:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.79,0:09:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one in the \Ngovernment who fought for the citizens!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.12,0:09:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when it almost killed you!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.50,0:09:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph! You should've died...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.84,0:09:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,as the Captain of Drum Kingdom's Security Guard!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.33,0:09:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised that you survived in \Nthis country without any doctors.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.43,0:09:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Drum is acknowledged internationally \Nas a country with advanced medicine.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.64,0:09:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But who would know... that there \Nwere actually only 20 doctors,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.93,0:09:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,who worked in the research \Nfacility of the King's castle,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.81,0:09:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and all the other doctors were exiled?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.66,0:09:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.27,0:09:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who become sick can beg for their lives.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.36,0:10:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If I feel like it, I might lend them the Twenty MDs.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.33,0:10:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If they don't wanna die, all they \Nhave to do is obey me, the king!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.79,0:10:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, my ruling is perfect.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.58,0:10:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the government of this country!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.63,0:10:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't call that a government!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.38,0:10:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph! \NYou sure speak your mind, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.38,0:10:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him! Kill your ex-captain!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.72,0:10:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,As I figured, you don't get what I'm saying...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.81,0:10:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the son of the previous \Nking who was good to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.03,0:10:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping that you'd come to your senses some day,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but it seems like that was wishful thinking!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.11,0:10:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! There he goes! Ox-Ox Fruit!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.62,0:10:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The model "Bison"!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.37,0:10:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't flinch! Fire!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.83,0:10:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't hit him!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.83,0:10:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dodging them!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.79,0:10:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show no mercy even though \Nyou're my ex-subordinates!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fiddle Bam!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.43,0:11:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's strong! How powerful!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.02,0:11:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the wild power... \Nthe power of a Zoan type devil fruit...!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.98,0:11:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough with you all.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.69,0:11:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A country where the king is the first to run off
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.07,0:11:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,when the country is in crisis should just die out!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.99,0:11:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have a chance, \Nfighting against the two of us.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give up.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.58,0:11:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.87,0:11:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We've come to assist you!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.25,0:11:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us fight with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.88,0:11:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll protect this free country!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.88,0:11:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Above all, I've known you so long.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.80,0:11:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unfortunate for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.53,0:11:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your weak point is...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.95,0:12:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...did you shield us...?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.16,0:12:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.20,0:12:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.79,0:12:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dalton-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.18,0:12:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your weak point, kind Dalton-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.42,0:12:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a death befitting you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.84,0:12:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What's going on? An earthquake?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.64,0:12:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this isn't good. \NWe can't go further because of the deep snow.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.35,0:12:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we went up the mountain...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.73,0:12:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.78,0:12:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's... this rumbling?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp-{\i1}san{\i0}! Could this be...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.49,0:12:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh... A.. Avalanche...?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.25,0:12:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,25631... 25632...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,25633...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What's going on? How noisy...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.81,0:13:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,25634...!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.29,0:13:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! We're not high enough!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.17,0:13:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do now?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.89,0:13:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.18,0:13:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji! Grab my hand!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.69,0:13:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved my skin!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.15,0:14:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,even though we won't sink in the snow,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.15,0:14:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll go straight down the mountain \Nif we don't do anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.61,0:14:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.17,0:14:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell no! \NWe've come all this way and were almost
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.16,0:14:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,at the foot of that chimney mountain!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just a step away from the doctor!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.37,0:14:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Come up with a way to stop this!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.08,0:14:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, those damn hopping bunnies!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.59,0:14:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time I see them, \NI'll simmer them in a pot!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.89,0:14:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What're we gonna do, Sanji?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.14,0:14:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one way!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.23,0:14:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.40,0:14:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck's... with them?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.49,0:14:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Luffy! Look ahead! Ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.46,0:15:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! A rock! We're gonna crash!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.09,0:15:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't crash! \NYou're carrying Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's easy to say, but...!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.90,0:15:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We're crashing!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.74,0:15:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to treat ladies... gently!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.87,0:15:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.43,0:15:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh... That hit me good...! Dammit!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.30,0:15:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! \NDon't do stuff like that without telling me!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.98,0:16:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! Sanji!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! It's coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.29,0:16:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not stopping!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.83,0:16:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This village will be swallowed!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.41,0:16:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting out of here!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.13,0:16:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Chess! Kuromarimo! Get on!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.38,0:16:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Robson!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.88,0:16:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Robson, Serious Mode!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.76,0:16:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wapol-{\i1}sama{\i0}! \NPlease let us ride, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.23,0:16:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Get out of here on your own!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.94,0:16:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Robson! Hurry up! It's closing in on us!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.69,0:16:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-W-W-W-W-W-W-W-W-We'll be fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.49,0:16:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Vivi!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.58,0:16:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we get swallowed, I'll save you for sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.20,0:16:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you think Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0} and the others...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.62,0:17:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Could they have been \Nswallowed by this avalanche?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.12,0:17:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhhh! Wapol-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.21,0:17:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.50,0:17:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.92,0:17:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.51,0:17:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhhhh!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.78,0:18:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami, are you cold? \NHang in there just a little longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.45,0:18:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. Hold this.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.08,0:18:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here and wait for me a little longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was you guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.87,0:19:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder I thought it was an awful syrup.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.96,0:19:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll never get away with this!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.67,0:19:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.05,0:19:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Of course {\i1}them{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.79,0:19:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Them meaning...?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.43,0:19:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You said some Straw Hats
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.30,0:19:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,are going up the mountain \Nto the castle right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.22,0:19:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this is what happened!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.43,0:19:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They have a huge grudge against \Nus over what happened between us,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.40,0:19:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so they caused an avalanche \Non that snow mountain.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.32,0:19:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! That's what happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.57,0:19:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, this avalanche was their doing...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.53,0:19:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! \NWe'll follow them on the snow mountain!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.53,0:19:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach them a lesson \Nabout battling in the snow!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.29,0:21:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I will definitely get you there.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.34,0:21:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,both of you...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.35,0:21:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.22,0:21:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please look at that, Wapol-{\i1}sama{\i0}! \NWe found them!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.60,0:21:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, brat!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.06,0:21:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you do many rude things to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.77,0:21:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll beat you up!
